Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.67,0:01:06.86,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:10.23,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.35,0:01:16.56,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}倘若能彼此交心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.96,0:01:24.90,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自那天起 四季更替时光流转
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:30.69,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我只想说 谢谢你伴我至今
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:38.90,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}呵着白气 朝向狭窄的小巷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:44.29,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你温暖的手使劲拉着我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:46.25,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不断前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:49.45,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}好想马上就亲吻你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:53.15,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}躲在自动售货机背后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:56.60,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}害羞地凝视对方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:02:02.04,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}温柔的心情洋溢胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:05.57,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:09.02,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:14.46,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}倘若能彼此交心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:16.61,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我们便能融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:19.81,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}与一份小小幸福的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:23.36,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}似乎就在触手可及的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:26.09,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}能变得如此温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.05,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}全因有你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------EDCN5-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.52,0:22:27.72,EDCN6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}霓虹灯的蓝光 妆点着人行道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.11,0:22:35.35,EDCN6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}热闹的人群中 我独自伫立
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:39.63,EDCN6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}写满快乐的一张张笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.76,0:22:44.12,EDCN6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}相互依偎的一对对恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.37,0:22:48.56,EDCN6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}对此刻的我而言 这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:53.48,EDCN6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}都太过耀眼 而不能直视
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.65,0:23:00.70,EDCN6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}有人会爱我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.76,0:23:11.09,EDCN6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}谁来察觉藏在坚强背后的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.33,0:23:17.02,EDCN6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}真的能获得自由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.28,0:23:20.12,EDCN6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.28,0:23:27.45,EDCN6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}冬日的街道上 误入人间的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.86,0:23:37.10,EDCN6,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}正温柔地轻声叹息
