Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.12,0:00:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创设祭的准备工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.63,0:00:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进度似乎比预定的慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是慢了点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还可以赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.73,0:00:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.61,0:00:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 绚辻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你前段时间不是病倒了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事在教职员会议里成为问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说想缩小创设祭的规模
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如将圣诞树的装饰灯去掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.75,0:00:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是减少活动的数目什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位执行委员都在努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能请你们再继续观察一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 不过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:00:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要勉强自己 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.23,0:01:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我明白
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屈辱 太屈辱了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会被老师被叫去 还提醒我注意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是大家能再能干一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用这么辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有责怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师说我们的进度慢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想将圣诞树的装饰灯去掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都这么期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会尽力协助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么问题么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间确实是不够
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了你有没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 橘学长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们找不到主舞台的照明灯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我记得资材仓库里有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有点重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘 我这边一个人能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去帮她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天吃了太多肉包子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来我花了一晚来想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下那么点时间该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就是没什么好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你有没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么一脸悠然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻为了我做便当过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好吃 好吃极了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗表演了杂技 给点奖励也是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是预付款
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我是狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这个了 有没有什么好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我觉得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好还是增加人手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太没面子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:05:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今再说人手不够 请求支援什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的尊严可不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样下去就来不及了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说我们这些执行委员辛苦点也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可老师也说不要太勉强嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以正面解决不是最好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 让大家帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统筹好 让创设祭成功了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的评价应该也会上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在统率能力方面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统率能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 似乎只有这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 那先叫咱班帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过在此之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实之前我也考虑过增加人手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要没收这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 炸鸡是我留着最后吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经吃掉了 不还了～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:05:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻和橘？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 干不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 为什么我们非得干这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们自己报名要当执行委员的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给我们这边添麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家肯定忙着二人世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻和橘午休时恩恩爱爱地吃便当
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 开会开太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说圣诞树不要了 是不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了个比去年还要华丽的创设祭计划
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却似乎没法顺利完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在再找大家帮忙是作何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 功劳就归你这个执行委员长？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如意算盘打得太响了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没这个打算…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进度慢 是忙着跟某男生拍拖造成的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们总是单独两个干活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像男女朋友一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为橘要帮我做工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可能让你们误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们没做过工作以外的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们这些人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棚町你别出声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我能力差 绚辻只是在教我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没问你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了绚辻 说句话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 难道弄哭你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 愚蠢之极
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们说的 跟创设祭一点关系都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么 嫉妒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你们一个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞树会照样弄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和去年相比 进度也足够跟得上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家帮忙 只是为了确保其成功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不信的话 随便你们看资料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有你们这种人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会听信毫无根据的谣言 跟着瞎抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都做不成却看不起人 优越感爆棚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无不无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要还口的话 请随意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你们做得到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有胜得过我的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道「羞」字怎么写的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回顾一下自己的人生后再说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 想说就说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那最开始就不要说些无聊的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都动手就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你们就只会做这些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那话说得太过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 记得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻 你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说已经没必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了自己有更重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听我说么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 是不是有点太简短了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有点 是非常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.69,0:10:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归你了是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你一起 挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 连我自己都有点不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:11:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话 想一直都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你在身边的话 就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我不能强制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 把我给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对的 把有你在的生活给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我够格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好话不说两遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清楚回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌弃我的话 乐意至极
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这是契约的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样契约就生效了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点紧张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 收拾完现场回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 绚辻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻也会兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜 还在火辣辣地痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻 早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天执行委员会议要用的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:12:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都整理好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯 做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说有事 让我们跑十圈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说老师也太偷工减料了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算注意到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻那队处于下风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内野怎么才一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 似乎那队就一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了 得快点跑完十圈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 香苗 看那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁班好像有点麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 怎么了 已经累透了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还干劲十足嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 棚町 干掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这队太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要加入这队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 棚町
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用帮我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说 让我也享受一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 惠子 你也过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就有3个了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是4个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧 绚辻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 女生玩闪避球你掺和啥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要跑的十圈已经跑完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊着呢 让我也加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:15:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你上气不接下气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真帅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅哦 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 橘 你太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想玩 你们自己玩个够
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就玩完了 真没劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 必要的东西都下单了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 接下来就是等货到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是又完成一件工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都说有事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 有少数精锐部队就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我们几个动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:16:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我连走掉的人的活儿也干了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该出手时还是很能干的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别迷上我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真累
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我估计还是第一次在学校留这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 接下去要不要到哪里逛逛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 真的假的 我已经累虚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 快点回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像落下东西在教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 你先回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以努力 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然一个人在干活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:16:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说一句 我肯定会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 我已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是再拜托一下大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们帮忙比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去肯定赶不及
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅原他们也有帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你也明白人手还是不够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时我通宵也会干好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再病倒怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我绝对不干
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 你平常都是堂堂正正
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也总是能漂亮地打破这种局面的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 其实是在变成这种局面之前就更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像我是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有多了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啊 到底有多了解我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你为了创设祭很拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 跟大家道个歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托大家帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不愿意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在可能的范围内减少活动数目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你明明知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要说这种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个会不会更好看一点？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:19:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,树顶反正看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用装饰灯和丝带怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样装点起来也轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 把人偶放在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子也会开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 还好跟大家商量了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.29,0:19:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也没亲眼看到…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么突然啊 你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前是我说得太过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果原谅我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能请你们帮忙准备创设祭？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了那么过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道歉也不原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我想让创设祭成功
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和大家一起快乐地做准备工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄哭她了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻虽然是过分了点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们也一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 体育课那时也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都道歉了 原谅她不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦 我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也说得太过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会帮忙准备创设祭的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬起头来 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的 我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 虽然我也觉得假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊 橘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.49,0:20:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会帮忙准备创设祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大家都是好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能在这班上实在太幸运了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 叫我到这地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会又要亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 虽然那个也挺有吸引力的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说这个了 到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天跟你说让全班来帮忙 还那么不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还扇了我一耳光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我指什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你是说她么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固执地想一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶在时限前做好准备工作的那个她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你认识的她已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜其所赐 大家都肯来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次创设祭肯定会超成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.04,0:23:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.55,0:23:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘 还差一点就到创设祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.70,0:23:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.30,0:23:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟班上同学也和好如初了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.77,0:23:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创设祭的准备工作 肯定会很顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.36,0:23:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.81,0:23:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过一个美妙的创设祭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.34,0:23:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安夜又要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.38,0:24:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 约定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.52,0:24:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的绚辻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.61,0:24:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.68,0:24:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.19,0:24:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.44,0:24:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里
